column34:
On 6/1/2022 Amber Heard lost her defamation trial against ex-husband Johnny Depp. 
Her vulgar accusations of domestic violence and sexual abuse she accused Johnny Depp of was proven by a jury to be false and used to defame Johnny Depp.

She lied under oath, making a mockery of the justice system and the true survivors of DV. 
Amber Heard needs to be held accountable for her actions and the damage she has caused just like anyone else would be.

She committed perjury, and will continue to do so if she is not held accountable for her breaking the law. 
Amber Heard should have the same punishment as any other American knowingly committing perjury. 

Let the whole world stand up, the true victims of DV and sign this petition to let her know that she is not above the law, and there are consequences.

she has hurt too many people, she needs to be stopped
